summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of East Sixty-fifth Street from Weedin Place to Fifteenth Avenue N.E. in the City of Seattle, by grading & curbing under Ordinance No. 18343, creating Local Improvement District No. 1732 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
